playlists.description: Mood Music for RPG and Inspiration. Inspired by the music of "Mass Effect", Interstellar is a collective of instrumental music that is reminiscent of space travel and combat. The general mood of the playlist is calm and peaceful, with faster-paced and tense tracks intermixed.
